  1.  Prerequisites

  This OS template requires Virtuozzo version 4.0.0 or later
  with deb2vzdeb version 4.0.0-4.swsoft or later, or
  Virtuozzo version 3.0.0 with vztt-3.0.0-70 or later.

  Please note that this templates have some requirements to Container
  resources which are covered by sample Container config named 'basic'.
  Additionally you should set lockedpages to 1024:1024.

  Also, vzpkgenvdeb version 4.6.0-2 or later required.

  2. Known issues

  You need to reboot the Container after upgrade from Ubuntu 8.04 or 9.10
  manually or use vztt 4.0.0-239 or later.

  vzctl start CTID --wait work on vzctl 4.0.0-239 or later.

